Material Calculators

Converting length, volume, weight or area measurements is often a time consuming task, so we have created a range of calculators to help make estimating a quick and easy process.

Our material calculators include estimators for aggregates, bricks and blocks, decking, flooring, insulation, paving, radiators (BTU) and tiling to ensure you are covered for all eventualities.

To get started, please find the material of interest and click the respective 'calculate button' below.
